#### PR description:

Updated KBMTF coarse eta assignments in the bmtf/omtf regions. New LUTs can be found in L1Trigger/L1TMuon/data/bmtf_luts/kalmanLUTs_v302.root, the config file has been modified accordingly.

Needed for next MWGR. Will be backported to 11_3_X
